<task xml:lang="en-us" id="task_7C08DE35754A4E9CBD45408A2B742B77">
    <title>Registering a Technical Service</title>
    <taskbody>
        <context>
            <p>By registering an application as a technical service, you make it available in <ph
                    conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/>. </p>
            <p>To register a technical service:</p>
        </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
                <cmd>Log in to the <ph conref="../../Shared/Product_Name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    /> administration portal.</cmd>
            </step>
            <step>
                <cmd>Do one of the following: </cmd>
                <choices>
                    <choice>Select <uicontrol>Technical Service</uicontrol> &gt;
                            <uicontrol>Register service definition</uicontrol>, and fill in the fields as desired.</choice>
                    <choice>Select <uicontrol>Technical Service</uicontrol> &gt;
                            <uicontrol>Import service definition</uicontrol>, and import the XML file containing your service definition.<p audience="doc">For details on how to create a technical service definition, refer to <xref
                                href="t_PrepareServDef.xml"/>.</p></choice>
                </choices>
            </step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
